{"children": [{"object": "block", "type": "heading_1", "heading_1": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "📊 AI日报 | 2026-03-01"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_2", "heading_2": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "🚀 模型速报"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Nano Banana 2（Gemini 3.1 Flash Image）"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Google正式发布第二代图像生成模型，主打「Pro级质量 + Flash级速度」，支持4K分辨率输出，文字渲染显著提升，已替换为Gemini和Google Search的默认图像引擎。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "TechRadar", "link": {"url": "https://www.techradar.com"}}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": " / "}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "MoneyControl", "link": {"url": "https://www.moneycontrol.com"}}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": " / "}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Geeky Gadgets", "link": {"url": "https://www.geeky-gadgets.com"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Claude Opus 4.6 / Sonnet 4.6"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Anthropic在2026年2月先后发布了Claude Opus 4.6和Sonnet 4.6，属于本月已落地的新模型版本，仍是编程场景头部选手。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Wikipedia", "link": {"url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_(language_model)"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "DeepSeek V4（即将发布）"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "据路透社消息，DeepSeek正在筹备V4发布，预计3月上线。争议点：提前向华为等国内芯片商开放适配权限，刻意绕开Nvidia和AMD。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "PC Gamer", "link": {"url": "https://www.pcgamer.com/software/ai/deepseek-has-reportedly-denied-nvidia-and-amd-early-access-to-its-new-v4-ai-model-giving-huawei-and-other-chinese-chipmakers-a-head-start/"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Grok 4.1 Fast"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "xAI的Grok 4.0正式在Microsoft Azure Foundry上线GA，同时推出Grok 4.1 Fast版本，主打速度和增强能力。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Microsoft Tech Community", "link": {"url": "https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azure-ai-foundry-blog/grok-4-0-goes-ga-in-microsoft-foundry-and-grok-4-1-fast-arrives-with-major-enhan/4497964"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_2", "heading_2": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "🛠️ AI工具 & 应用"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Claude iOS App冲上App Store第2"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "因五角大楼风波，Anthropic Claude在Apple美区App Store冲到#2（仅次于ChatGPT，超过Google Gemini），2月初排名还在100名开外。说明一件事：争议即流量，价值观站位也能带来用户。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "TechCrunch", "link": {"url": "https://techcrunch.com/2026/02/28/anthropics-claude-rises-to-no-2-in-the-app-store-following-pentagon-dispute/"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "OpenAI × 美国国防部"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "OpenAI趁Anthropic被踢出军方合同的空档，正式签署协议将其模型部署进五角大楼涉密云网络。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Reuters", "link": {"url": "https://www.reuters.com"}}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": " / "}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Bloomberg", "link": {"url": "https://www.bloomberg.com"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "OpenHunt"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Product Hunt上线AI原生发现层工具，由多个自主AI Agent对新产品进行多角度分析，旨在取代传统的人工投票机制。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Product Hunt", "link": {"url": "https://www.producthunt.com/products/openhunt"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_2", "heading_2": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "👀 博主精读"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "@sama（Sam Altman）"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "五角大楼封禁Anthropic后数小时，Altman迅速表态：OpenAI与Anthropic持相同的红线（不允许用于大规模国内监控和全自主武器），随即拿下五角大楼合同，并表示会向Pentagon派驻工程师确保模型安全。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "核心观点："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "这已不只是Anthropic的问题，而是整个行业需要厘清立场的时刻。"}, "annotations": {"italic": true}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Axios", "link": {"url": "https://www.axios.com/2026/02/27/altman-openai-anthropic-pentagon"}}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": " / "}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "CNN", "link": {"url": "https://www.cnn.com/2026/02/27/tech/openai-has-same-redlines-as-anthropic-in-any-deal-with-the-pentagon"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "MIT研究团队"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "发布报告：多数AI Agent系统既不披露安全测试细节，也没有关掉失控Bot的文档化机制。研究发现Agent之间相互交互时甚至会引发服务器崩溃和DoS攻击。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "ZDNet", "link": {"url": "https://www.zdnet.com"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_2", "heading_2": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "🔧 MCP & Agent Skills 精选"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Composio × Claude Agent SDK"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Composio推出Claude Agent SDK的MCP工具整合文档，可把Miro、Notion等SaaS工具一键接入Claude Agent，适合想搭建自动化工作流的个人开发者。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "composio.dev", "link": {"url": "https://composio.dev"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "OpenCode vs Claude Code"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "开源编程Agent生态已成气候：OpenCode（MIT协议，Rust重写，62K stars）+ Claude Code（Anthropic官方，MCP深度集成）是当前编程Agent的两强格局。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "morphllm.com", "link": {"url": "https://morphllm.com"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Anthropic爆料中国AI公司抄袭"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Anthropic爆料DeepSeek、Moonshot AI、MiniMax通过1600万次Claude API调用工业规模抄袭其模型能力，可能涉及违反API服务条款。Anthropic正在加强滥用监控，对做Agent开发的开发者是个信号。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "来源："}}, {"type": "text", "text": {"content": "The Hacker News", "link": {"url": "https://thehackernews.com/2026/02/anthropic-says-chinese-ai-firms-used-16.html"}}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_2", "heading_2": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "💡 今日选题"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "选题1（强推）：Anthropic拒绝帮军队造武器，反被封杀，然后火了"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "切入点：AI公司的价值观边界 vs 商业利益。Anthropic坚持不用于大规模监控/自主武器，被Trump政府列为威胁，Claude在App Store爆火。这个故事弧线完美，适合「普通人也能看懂的AI大事件」系列。角度：不是批评谁，而是讲坚持原则在商业上的反向收益。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "选题2（技术向）：你的AI助手可能根本没有关机开关"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "切入点：MIT报告直指Agent失控风险，多数系统连安全测试记录都没有。适合做深夜开发者视角的冷静分析：我们在加速上Agent，但底层安全框架还没跟上。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "选题3：DeepSeek V4的国产优先——中美AI芯片战最新战局"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "切入点：DeepSeek提前给华为开绿灯、把Nvidia排在门外，中国AI生态正在系统性去美化。给开发者的启示：AI基础设施的地缘政治风险正在变成现实影响。"}}]}}, {"object": "block", "type": "divider", "divider": {}}, {"object": "block", "type": "paragraph", "paragraph": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "以上由零零壹日报自动生成"}, "annotations": {"italic": true, "color": "gray"}}]}}]}